_Struct is a class that is used to get easy access to structures and its members.

sizeof() is used to calculate structure size and is mandatory for _Struct to work.

Read about usage of _Struct here: http://www.autohotkey.net/~HotKeyIt/AutoHotkey/_Struct.htm
Read about usage of sizeof  here: http://www.autohotkey.net/~HotKeyIt/AutoHotkey/sizeof.htm


Download _Struct.ahk and sizeof.ahk to your library (Path of AutoHotkey.exe\Lib\_Struct.ahk...)

Visit _Struct on AutoHotkey forum http://www.autohotkey.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=364838#364838!